{"tid":2505312,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"元朗警員遺失記事簿 記載市民個人資料或外洩","createTime":"2021-04-26T13:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T13:43:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4dedfe71e9a6294dc9f4f6ccbbba15d3f5a478cf","tid":2505312,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:11:34.000Z","msg":"一名隸屬鐵路警區巡邏小隊的男警務人員，昨日（25日）在元朗警署內發現遺失一本「警察記事簿」。警方接報後立即調查，並在可能遺失地點搜尋，暫未有發現。案件由鐵路警區跟進調查，<br />\n<br />\n警方提到，記事簿內記載了有關警員執勤期間紀錄，當中涉及個人資料。鐵路警區正嘗試通知受影響人士，並會風險評估，如有需要會考慮通知私隱專員。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲市民如拾獲該本記事簿，應立即致電九九九，或交到就近警署。警方提到，會就事件展開內部調查，強調如有人員違規，會嚴肅處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210426/3D4G3G57D5ALRGR4BWNX4HHWJY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210426%2F3D4G3G57D5ALRGR4BWNX4HHWJY%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6zbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=c213cea6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210426%2F3D4G3G57D5ALRGR4BWNX4HHWJY%2F&h=564143e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210426/3D4G3G57D5ALRGR4BWNX4HHWJY/</a>"},{"pid":"c3bba9dbd583584282a33e115af66e46cfa0aad0","tid":2505312,"uid":44211,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-IFongwCk3WA/VYwISMbzG9I/AAAAAAAAAeo/xcw7XrtQEmQ/s1600/74206.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-IFongwCk3WA%2FVYwISMbzG9I%2FAAAAAAAAAeo%2Fxcw7XrtQEmQ%2Fs1600%2F74206.png&h=97203789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑警殺人放火都唔會錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0118697008d0ce4a60821d4a927cc513f4f20591","tid":2505312,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3bba9dbd583584282a33e115af66e46cfa0aad0","tid":2505312,"uid":44211,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"ht